<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99368955666493></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99368955666493><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=99368955666493>RE: Everyone says Bard....</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=99368955666493#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=65118><span id= >rokgoblin</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Jun 27th 8:52 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Some people have noting better to do that to stir up a confrontation in a discussion thread.&nbsp;&nbsp;It would be my guess that the person who posted this message is somwhere between 10 - 14 years old with a very small and under-utilized brain.  <br><br>Bards ROCK!!!! Literally :)  <br><br>So what if we run around all day singing "looking like sissies" as you said.  You would if you could.  Especially if all you have to do is sing (Chords of Dissonance - AoE & DoT - Lvl 2) and wait for the beasties to come then keep singing while slashing away.  Of course, we are not pure warriors or tanks, so it helps to have a fast attack weapon with good DMG if you want to solo.  Groups are a much better way for Bards to gain EXP though.<br><br>Bottom line: Bards are very useful in a group situation.  Their skills cannot be matched and thier group effects are unbeatable.  Lets see, can your warrior or whatever melee class you are playing heal the entire group at once, or let's see can you buff the entire groups AC, STR and DEX at level 1?  NOT!!!  <br><br>You should respect your friendly neighborhood Bard, (s)he makes an invaluable member to almost any group.  Especially if there are casters (which there almost always are) since they have mana regen song too.<br><br>TheGMan<br>Twister of the 5th off-key Song<br>&nbsp;<br>!~!rokgoblin<br>AKA. The G-Man of Spring<br><br>"If at first you don't succeed, skydiving is not for you."</td></tr>
